            "questionText": "A delivery drone starts from rest and ascends vertically with a constant acceleration of $!$2 \\frac{m}{s^2}$!$ for $!$10$!$ seconds. Then, it flies horizontally at a constant velocity for $!$30$!$ seconds before decelerating horizontally at $!$1 \\frac{m}{s^2}$!$ for $!$15$!$ seconds to land. Calculate the magnitude of the final displacement between the drone\u2019s landing position and its initial position at the warehouse.",
            "imageText": "",
            "steps": [
                {
                    "id": "a9a40ae54213432ca77ac",
